SubjectRegulations Respecting Fees for the Review of Arrangements Involving Transportation Undertakings Providing Air Services
PrecisREGULATIONS RESPECTING FEES FOR THE REVIEW OF ARRANGEMENTS INVOLVING TRANSPORTATION UNDERTAKINGS PROVIDING AIR SERVICES in order to enable the Minister of Transport to recover a portion of the costs associated with private benefits that a Transport Canada's assessment of air carrier joint ventures may lead to.
